{"tid":1648202,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警逃亡潮","createTime":"2019-10-12T05:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T06:23:43.000Z","uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bcf79f06b2af043d684a79e19ed9beb984d20cb","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"移民中介表示最近有好多黑警申請投資移民去台灣。<br />\n邊撚到俾你班黑警走得咁容易，有冇手足可以做野。<br />\n留班黑警係大灣區。"},{"pid":"3b721db7be6dae2d5ebb8c303bf11ac867eea81a","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"52de224d88c21d01e23a7483c7f21f1e35a460ce","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b5fd29a6af65b3e00059cc572b2ff0b9c764714d","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"6023b0f790c23bec83ff1ecea91a4b43c389ba1b","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"72e32357031add34b0a9e2e83dca210cd84bf10c","tid":1648202,"uid":329834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"833013e49717a947d1db6d7f785c30cdfbf79491","tid":1648202,"uid":230345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61acbe8b276be1aa27b0560d2fbda2c62e46bb27","tid":1648202,"uid":274815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n黑警集體逃亡，佢哋有一定人數，而且一定會有聯繫，過到去班廢柴冇嘢撈，好有可能會成立一鼓勢力。而佢哋有警察嘅訓練，亦可能係當地幫派嘅招攬對像。黑警係我哋仇人，唔可以比佢哋走，亦唔可以比佢哋喺台灣坐大，成為老共喺台灣嘅一鼓勢力。如果香港要變成地獄，香港人都要同你攬住死，一齊喺地獄萬劫不復。"}]}